# single_bet_ev.ts — Math Lockdown

Do NOT modify the mathematical formulas or logic in this file without a formal peer-review/approval step.

Protected:
- americanToDecimal, decimalToAmerican conversion formulas.
- calculateImpliedProbability = 1/decimalOdds; calculateFairOdds = 1/trueProb.
- calculateSingleBetEV = p*netProfit - (1-p); netProfit = decimalOdds - 1.
- calculateKellyFraction = (bp - q)/b; clamp [0,1]; 0 if EV<=0.

Allowed without approval: comments. No changes to equations.
